Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,制暴: 無限殺機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Boss. This for you.  - No, no, no. Come on.\N{\rDefault}- 老闆 這是給你的  - 不 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:44.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't impose on your family.\N{\rDefault}我不能麻煩你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rDefault}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:49.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yasmin, she made this just for you.\N{\rDefault}雅斯敏特意為你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jefe, please.\N{\rDefault}老闆 請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take it.\N{\rDefault}拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:54.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell her thank you.\N{\rDefault}替我謝謝她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:57.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rDefault}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, listen.\N{\rDefault}聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Today's gonna be hard.\N{\rDefault}今天會很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,We got inspections all day.\N{\rDefault}全天都有檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Forms to build, forms to break down\N{\rDefault}要填表 拆表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:09.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,and deliveries all gettin' in our way.\N{\rDefault}還有送貨的來添亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,We work hard today,\N{\rDefault}今天努力幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,there'll be a bonus for ya.\N{\rDefault}還會有獎金拿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,And let's all go home\N{\rDefault}咱們都得完好無損
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,with the same amount of fingers that we came with.\N{\rDefault}回家 一根手指都不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rDefault}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hermanos.\N{\rDefault}兄弟們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Have a good day. Let's get it.\N{\rDefault}祝今天順利 開工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Morning, Jess.  - Buenos dias, Levon.\N{\rDefault}- 早啊 潔茜  - 早 萊文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How you doing?  - I'm good.\N{\rDefault}- 你怎麼樣?  - 挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Gracias.  - Hey, Levon.\N{\rDefault}- 謝謝  - 嘿 萊文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:49.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,No one's been asking you for money today?\N{\rDefault}今天沒人跟你要錢吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:50.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rDefault}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Why?  - Because, apparently,\N{\rDefault}- 怎麼了?  - 因為很顯然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I am the only person in the family\N{\rDefault}全家只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,who can do the vendor accounting.\N{\rDefault}會做供應商賬目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:56.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me!\N{\rDefault}真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, I guess we're evil parents, babe, huh?\N{\rDefault}嘿 看來咱倆是邪惡父母啊 親愛的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,'Cause we make her work a couple hours.\N{\rDefault}就因為我們要她幹兩小時活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not today.\N{\rDefault}今天不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:03.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,How about you get those disbursements done, huh?\N{\rDefault}先把那些款項支付搞定如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,We got a line of trucks out there that need paying.\N{\rDefault}外面一堆卡車等著結賬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,You could pay me.\N{\rDefault}你可以先付我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pay you for what?\N{\rDefault}付你什麼錢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,For 19 years of free rent,\N{\rDefault}付我19年的免費房租
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,and groceries, and high school,\N{\rDefault}食品雜貨 中學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,college, makeup, karate classes?\N{\rDefault}大學 化妝品 空手道課?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You want me to keep goin'?  - Really? No. It's okay.\N{\rDefault}- 要我繼續列舉嗎?  - 認真的? 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:17.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Levon, can you sign that, please?\N{\rDefault}萊文 能籤個字嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Dad?  - What?\N{\rDefault}- 爸?  - 幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Today is a total shitshow.  - I know.\N{\rDefault}- 今天簡直一團糟  - 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you scheduled three things at once.\N{\rDefault}你還同時安排了三件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:24.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's not wrong.\N{\rDefault}她說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, yeah. This is Garcia and Family Construction.\N{\rDefault}嗨 這裏是加西亞家族建築公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're speaking with Carla,\N{\rDefault}我是卡拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,you've had me on hold for a bit now.\N{\rDefault}你們讓我等了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, we're gettin' those deliveries today, right?\N{\rDefault}今天能送貨對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll hold.\N{\rDefault}好 我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is what I need for tonight.\N{\rDefault}這是今晚要用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:41.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's insane. What is that? Is that for your wedding or something?\N{\rDefault}瘋了吧? 這是什麼? 你結婚啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, it's for tonight.\N{\rDefault}不 就今晚用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,We finished the semester, so we're gonna celebrate.\N{\rDefault}學期結束了 我們要慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, you just finished one semester.\N{\rDefault}你纔剛結束一個學期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Right. It's a big milestone.  - Is it?\N{\rDefault}- 對 這是重要里程碑  - 是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes.  - Is that a thing?\N{\rDefault}- 是啊  - 有這說法?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look, it could be worse, okay?\N{\rDefault}聽著 情況可能更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Look, I'm passing the hat.  - Mm-hmm. Yeah.\N{\rDefault}- 我在籌錢  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That gets us a party van.  - Oh, my God.\N{\rDefault}- 夠租派對巴士了  - 天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Locks in a private room for dinner.\N{\rDefault}還能訂餐廳包間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:58.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just saving like crazy.\N{\rDefault}拼命省錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I just need a card on file.\N{\rDefault}對 只需要一張信用卡擔保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mija, I can't. I don't...\N{\rDefault}女兒 我做不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:04.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mija...\N{\rDefault}女兒...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. I don't need it.\N{\rDefault}好吧 算了 我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just give her what she wants.\N{\rDefault}她要什麼就給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, Mom, I can fight my own battles.\N{\rDefault}不 媽 我能自己爭取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, nobody's arguing that.\N{\rDefault}噢 不 沒人質疑這點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, everybody needs a party bus, right?\N{\rDefault}誰不需要派對巴士呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,After they finish one semester. Here.\N{\rDefault}尤其是剛結束一學期的時候 給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rDefault}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kate.\N{\rDefault}嘿 凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\N{\rDefault}借過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,He needs to get back to work.\N{\rDefault}他得回去幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get the fuck out of here. It's not your business.\N{\rDefault}滾你媽的 關你屁事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm good, boss.\N{\rDefault}我沒事 老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,All good. Five minutes.\N{\rDefault}沒事 五分鐘就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:16.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey!\N{\rDefault}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was respectful.\N{\rDefault}我很禮貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,You weren't.\N{\rDefault}你可沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get outta here. Get up.\N{\rDefault}滾出去 起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't come back.\N{\rDefault}別再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Vamonos.  - Vamonos.\N{\rDefault}- 走吧  - 走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,You okay?\N{\rDefault}你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,How did you do that?\N{\rDefault}你怎麼做到的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:08.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,We need to get back to work.\N{\rDefault}該回去幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,This one. Over to the right.\N{\rDefault}這個 搬到右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:13.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You got it.  - Thanks, Kate.\N{\rDefault}- 明白  - 謝了 凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Levon! Holy fuck!\N{\rDefault}萊文 臥槽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Was that some military shit?\N{\rDefault}那是軍隊的招式嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,You didn't see anything.\N{\rDefault}你什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,If Dad knew, he'd shit bricks.\N{\rDefault}要是爸知道 他會氣瘋的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you teach me?\N{\rDefault}能教我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look, my grandpa, he was a paratrooper.\N{\rDefault}我爺爺是傘兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Taught me how to break fingers,\N{\rDefault}他教我怎麼掰斷手指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,track animals.\N{\rDefault}追蹤動物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Break fingers?\N{\rDefault}掰斷手指?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rDefault}對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Grandma made you tinga. Shredded chicken.\N{\rDefault}奶奶給你做了廷加燉雞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:37.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's good.\N{\rDefault}很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:41.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,And Grandma made you some handmade grandma tortillas.\N{\rDefault}還有奶奶手工做的玉米餅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone always feeding me?\N{\rDefault}為啥總有人給我送吃的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we don't, you'll just eat canned tuna and peanut butter.\N{\rDefault}不給你送 你就只吃金槍魚罐頭和花生醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:51.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,You didn't see anything, okay?\N{\rDefault}你什麼都沒看到 懂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Snitches get stitches.\N{\rDefault}告密者沒有好下場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just get my back if I ever need it.\N{\rDefault}我需要時你得罩著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:55.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sure, Jenny.\N{\rDefault}沒問題 珍妮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,See ya.\N{\rDefault}回見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Love you, Daddy.\N{\rDefault}愛你 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Love you, too, honey. Get in the truck.\N{\rDefault}我也愛你 寶貝 上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's the occasion?\N{\rDefault}什麼大日子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,No occasion.\N{\rDefault}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Meredith's entertaining some friends.\N{\rDefault}梅雷迪思要招待朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:44.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rDefault}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize today was your visitation.\N{\rDefault}我不知道今天是你探視日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,You could let her stay.\N{\rDefault}你可以讓她留下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, please, Doctor Roth, we don't have to do this.\N{\rDefault}是 求你了 羅斯醫生 沒必要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,You weren't there when her mother needed you\N{\rDefault}她媽媽需要你時你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,and you won't be there when Meredith needs you,\N{\rDefault}梅雷迪思需要你時你也不會在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:58.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I will.\N{\rDefault}但我會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.\N{\rDefault}噢 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want to strike me.\N{\rDefault}你想打我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's your only answer.\N{\rDefault}你只會這一招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Violence.\N{\rDefault}暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're an unsafe parent.\N{\rDefault}你是個不合格的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're a killer.\N{\rDefault}你是殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:21.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't pretend that you're not.\N{\rDefault}別假裝你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Doctor Roth.\N{\rDefault}失陪了 羅斯醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Today's my day.\N{\rDefault}今天是我的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why's your grandfather throwing a party on my day?\N{\rDefault}你外公為什麼在我探視日開派對?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm super hungry. I didn't eat.\N{\rDefault}我餓死了 還沒吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you.\N{\rDefault}在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:48.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,You were?\N{\rDefault}真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:49.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rDefault}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go.\N{\rDefault}好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:55.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Here you go.  - Thank you.\N{\rDefault}- 給  - 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.  - Enjoy.\N{\rDefault}- 謝謝  - 慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't need you buying stuff.\N{\rDefault}不用你給我買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on. Open it.\N{\rDefault}來嘛 開啟看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Mama.\N{\rDefault}是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I took that picture\N{\rDefault}這張照片是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,with a film camera my dad gave me.\N{\rDefault}用我爸給的膠捲相機拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Grandpa took all of Mama's pictures down.\N{\rDefault}外公把媽媽的照片都收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I forget what she looks like.\N{\rDefault}有時候我都快忘了她的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,She looks like you.\N{\rDefault}你跟她很像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dad, can I tell you something?\N{\rDefault}爸 我能跟你說件事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anything.\N{\rDefault}什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm mad at Mama.\N{\rDefault}我生媽媽的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,For dying and leaving us.\N{\rDefault}她丟下我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay.\N{\rDefault}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hurt, too.\N{\rDefault}我也很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Matt will see you now.\N{\rDefault}馬特現在可以見你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's throwing parties for her during my visitation time.\N{\rDefault}他在我的探視時間給她辦派對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Staring at me, laughing.\N{\rDefault}盯著我 嘲笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's baiting you.\N{\rDefault}他在激怒你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hoping you throw a punch.\N{\rDefault}就等你揮拳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:36.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nah.\N{\rDefault}不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then he wins.\N{\rDefault}那他就得逞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:40.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Opposing counsel\N{\rDefault}對方律師稱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,alleges you have untreated PTSD\N{\rDefault}你因服役而患有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,and brain trauma from your military service,\N{\rDefault}創傷後應激障礙和腦部創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,making you at-risk for violence.\N{\rDefault}因此有暴力風險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,I served Britain, the country of my birth, for 22 years.\N{\rDefault}我為出生地英國效力22年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm the fuckin' bad guy for it?\N{\rDefault}反倒成壞人了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,It gets worse.\N{\rDefault}更糟的還在後面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're requesting supervised visits\N{\rDefault}他們要求探視需監督
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:06.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,and a reduction in visitation from two hours a week\N{\rDefault}並從每週兩小時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,to one hour every two.\N{\rDefault}減為每兩週一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have to fight this.\N{\rDefault}我必須抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have ten grand saved up.\N{\rDefault}我攢了一萬塊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,From sleeping in your truck?\N{\rDefault}睡卡車攢的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:14.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Court won't be thrilled\N{\rDefault}法庭不會喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,by your lack of a fixed residence.\N{\rDefault}居無定所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll figure it out.\N{\rDefault}嘿 我會解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why does Doctor Roth hate you so much?\N{\rDefault}羅斯醫生為什麼這麼恨你?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,He thinks I killed his daughter.\N{\rDefault}他覺得我害死了他女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:24.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did you?\N{\rDefault}你有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was suicide.\N{\rDefault}是自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was overseas on a deployment.\N{\rDefault}我當時在海外部署
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,She battled depression her whole life.\N{\rDefault}她一生都在對抗抑鬱症
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've heard of attrition warfare?\N{\rDefault}知道消耗戰嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You grind the enemy down slowly.\N{\rDefault}知道 慢慢拖垮敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,This guy's got a team\N{\rDefault}這傢伙有一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,of thousand-dollar-an-hour attorneys\N{\rDefault}時薪千刀的律師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,who will bleed you dry\N{\rDefault}會榨乾你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,until you turn to dust and blow away.\N{\rDefault}直到你化為塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,The best we can do is negotiated surrender.\N{\rDefault}我們最多爭取談判投降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:53.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have a daughter?\N{\rDefault}你有女兒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got you guys a little somethin'.\N{\rDefault}給你們帶了點小東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:09.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nina.\N{\rDefault}尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:10.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jocelyn...\N{\rDefault}喬斯琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Chantel. And Rubi.  - Thanks, Mama.\N{\rDefault}- 尚特爾 還有魯比  - 謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dude, these are insane!\N{\rDefault}老兄 這太絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get these?\N{\rDefault}哪弄來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have a cousin. Or seven.\N{\rDefault}我有幾個表親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Salud, bitches!\N{\rDefault}乾杯 混蛋們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rDefault}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:05.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,shots.\N{\rDefault}一口乾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey!\N{\rDefault}嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? What? What?\N{\rDefault}幹嘛? 幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the fuck are we still doing here?\N{\rDefault}我們還他媽在這幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,He said he wants the One.\N{\rDefault}他說他要「那個」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,"I want the One. I want the fucking One."\N{\rDefault}「我要那個 我他媽就要那個」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the fuck does that mean?\N{\rDefault}這他媽什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,He'll know it when he sees her, okay?\N{\rDefault}他看到就會知道 懂?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you know how much fuckin' money\N{\rDefault}你知道這單能賺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:49.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,we're gonna make on this?\N{\rDefault}多少錢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We better.  - Enjoy, yeah?\N{\rDefault}- 最好如此  - 享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, last establishment.\N{\rDefault}嘿 最後一站了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,You guys have early flights.\N{\rDefault}你們早班機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that back table open?\N{\rDefault}後面那張桌空著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's yours if you tell me your name.\N{\rDefault}告訴我名字就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:22.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Jenny.\N{\rDefault}我叫珍妮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Johnny.\N{\rDefault}嗨 我是喬尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, Johnny.\N{\rDefault}嗨 喬尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:29.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right here.\N{\rDefault}這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:43.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,My man.\N{\rDefault}老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,You are more than a pitch deck.\N{\rDefault}你比提案精彩多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nina?\N{\rDefault}尼娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Nina, don't throw up.  - I'm fine.\N{\rDefault}- 尼娜 別吐  - 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's making her puke face.\N{\rDefault}她要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Let's get you to a bathroom.  - Oh, ew.\N{\rDefault}- 帶她去洗手間  - 嘔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cheap! Bad energy.\N{\rDefault}廉價 晦氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:09.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ew!\N{\rDefault}嘔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.\N{\rDefault}天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hate you so much right now, it's not funny.\N{\rDefault}我現在恨死你了 一點不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:15.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's kinda funny.\N{\rDefault}有點好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, I look mad busted.\N{\rDefault}天 我妝都花了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,I cannot go out there like this.\N{\rDefault}這樣沒法見人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, pick your battles, 'cause we're leavin' in 30.\N{\rDefault}好吧 取捨一下吧 30分鐘後出發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fuck!\N{\rDefault}媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go.\N{\rDefault}走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny's missing.\N{\rDefault}珍妮失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "missing"?\N{\rDefault}怎麼「失蹤」了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,She went out with her friends on Friday.\N{\rDefault}她週五和朋友出去後就沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Saturday, we were worried,\N{\rDefault}週六 我們急了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,so we called the cops, and then on Sunday...\N{\rDefault}就報了警 週日...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,She had a piano recital on Sunday\N{\rDefault}她週日晚上有鋼琴演奏會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,We invited half our family.\N{\rDefault}我們請了半個家族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,My cousin Dinora is a Police Captain in Philly,\N{\rDefault}我表姐迪諾拉是費城警長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,and she says they don't work these cases.\N{\rDefault}她說警方不查這種案子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,They take a report and forget about it.\N{\rDefault}錄個口供就不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you help us?\N{\rDefault}你能幫我們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can keep the site running smoothly.\N{\rDefault}我可以維持工地正常運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. Help us find Jen.\N{\rDefault}不 幫我們找珍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:02.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,My dad was a Green Beret.\N{\rDefault}我爸是綠色貝雷帽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can see you guys comin' a mile away.\N{\rDefault}我一眼就看出你的底細
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,You hunt bad guys.\N{\rDefault}你們專抓壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,You jump outta planes.\N{\rDefault}你們從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you get those bad guys.\N{\rDefault}然後解決那些壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm a different person now.\N{\rDefault}我現在已經不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, well,\N{\rDefault}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,maybe this'll help her.\N{\rDefault}也許這個能幫到她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here, it's 50.\N{\rDefault}給 這是5萬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:31.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take it.\N{\rDefault}拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have another 20 for expenses.\N{\rDefault}還有2萬經費
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, just take it, man.\N{\rDefault}拿著吧 老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:35.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rDefault}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not who I am anymore.\N{\rDefault}我早就不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gunny, it's me!\N{\rDefault}甘尼 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:16.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me!\N{\rDefault}別殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got steaks!\N{\rDefault}我帶了牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you'd shot a foot to the left, I'd be dead.\N{\rDefault}你剛纔偏左一英尺我就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,If I wanted you dead, you'd be dead.\N{\rDefault}如果想殺你 你都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, for me,\N{\rDefault}知道嗎 對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:33.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,there's no separation between day and night.\N{\rDefault}晝夜沒有分別
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, I got to make my own.\N{\rDefault}所以我自己安排時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's hard livin' in a gray world.\N{\rDefault}活在灰暗的世界裏很難
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I couldn't save your eyes.\N{\rDefault}我救不了你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:41.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\N{\rDefault}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,That eats at me.\N{\rDefault}這事一直折磨我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:46.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rDefault}不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,You saved my life.\N{\rDefault}你救了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Joyce would be burying tags in the back yard\N{\rDefault}要不是你趕來救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,if you hadn't come along, scooped me up and ran.\N{\rDefault}喬伊斯早在後院給我立墓碑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:58.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's her name?\N{\rDefault}她叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:00.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny.\N{\rDefault}珍妮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:03.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny. All right.\N{\rDefault}珍妮 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,She a good kid?\N{\rDefault}她是個好孩子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's a great kid.\N{\rDefault}她非常優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, you do this, you better lock in.\N{\rDefault}既然要做 就必須全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:15.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,You better go full on, no half-measures.\N{\rDefault}不能半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you do, God help 'em.\N{\rDefault}但只要你堅持到底 上帝會保佑他們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:21.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told Jenny I had her back.\N{\rDefault}我答應過珍妮會保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...\N{\rDefault}呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I miss ya.\N{\rDefault}我想你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:29.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,I worry about ya,\N{\rDefault}我擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:33.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,but you didn't have to come down here and pretend that\N{\rDefault}但你也不必專程跑來來假裝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:35.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,you needed my permission for something\N{\rDefault}需要我批准
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,you already made your mind up about.\N{\rDefault}你早已決定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get in here. We're eating.\N{\rDefault}進來吧 吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:56.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Carla.\N{\rDefault}嘿 卡拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:57.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.\N{\rDefault}謝謝你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where is he?\N{\rDefault}他在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Upstairs. First door on your left.\N{\rDefault}樓上 左邊第一間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Moonlight Sonata".\N{\rDefault}「月光奏鳴曲」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:32.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,-Yeah.  - It's beautiful.\N{\rDefault}- 對  - 很美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,She turned down a music scholarship\N{\rDefault}她拒絕了音樂獎學金
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:35.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,to go to business school.\N{\rDefault}去讀了商學院
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,She wanted to be like her pops.\N{\rDefault}她想成為像她爸爸那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Be a big land developer.\N{\rDefault}當個大地產商
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:45.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,And she will.\N{\rDefault}她會的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:47.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rDefault}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:52.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nah. No, thanks.\N{\rDefault}不了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:57.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your family needs hope.\N{\rDefault}你的家人需要希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:22:59.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I can't face 'em like this.\N{\rDefault}但我不能這樣面對他們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:03.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,When my wife passed,\N{\rDefault}我妻子去世後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:07.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I left the Royal Marines,\N{\rDefault}我離開皇家海軍陸戰隊時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:09.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,a lot of people would've given up on me.\N{\rDefault}很多人都會放棄我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:12.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you were patient with me.\N{\rDefault}但你對我很有耐心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:17.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You, Carla, Jenny.  - Jenny.\N{\rDefault}- 你 卡拉 珍妮  - 珍妮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:21.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're my family.\N{\rDefault}你們是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:40.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at me, brother.\N{\rDefault}看著我 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:44.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna bring her home.\N{\rDefault}我會帶她回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.41,0:23:49.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,I promise.\N{\rDefault}我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:51.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna bring her home.\N{\rDefault}我會帶她回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:23:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,尋人：珍妮·加西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:20.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Skip's Bar."\N{\rDefault}「斯基普酒吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.87,0:24:45.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. Good, bro?\N{\rDefault}非常感謝 不錯吧 兄弟?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.21,0:24:49.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,You good? Yeah?\N{\rDefault}還行嗎? 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.85,0:24:53.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,How you doing?\N{\rDefault}你好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.07,0:24:56.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You need a little aperitif, you know?\N{\rDefault}你需要點餐前酒 懂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.28,0:24:59.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rDefault}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.05,0:27:17.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, yo. Wrong house, kid.\N{\rDefault}嘿 小子 走錯門了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.00,0:27:19.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get the fuck out.\N{\rDefault}滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.29,0:27:20.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, Johnny.\N{\rDefault}你好啊 喬尼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.30,0:27:23.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wanna have a race? See who wins?\N{\rDefault}想比誰更快嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.90,0:27:28.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hands up. Stand up.\N{\rDefault}舉手 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:30.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Place your fingers behind your head.\N{\rDefault}雙手抱頭
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.07,0:27:32.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,You a cop?\N{\rDefault}你是條子?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.30,0:27:33.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wish I was a cop.\N{\rDefault}你希望我是條子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.40,0:27:37.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your adventure, kid.\N{\rDefault}你的冒險 小子
